{"tid":491201,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"喵星人的電影世界","createTime":"2017-12-06T09:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T10:09:59.000Z","uid":40662,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb543fb2b7097876c08cbe905953bf0c563a1a4","tid":491201,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-V9Rpdt8Mun8/Wh1uMPL0-vI/AAAAAAAAP8k/zS6UxiyVpjAC6ugjCHTX0b5bVmfyfnxAACLcBGAs/s1600/3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-V9Rpdt8Mun8%2FWh1uMPL0-vI%2FAAAAAAAAP8k%2FzS6UxiyVpjAC6ugjCHTX0b5bVmfyfnxAACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F3.jpg&h=4201925c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n你行得上台唔好怯呀～怯，你就輸咗成世！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-D43Ht21pw_8/Wh1wMCA5mEI/AAAAAAAAP88/7QkLDtZb-DMguXJnHVpM957f3bdjN3ndACLcBGAs/s1600/6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-D43Ht21pw_8%2FWh1wMCA5mEI%2FAAAAAAAAP88%2F7QkLDtZb-DMguXJnHVpM957f3bdjN3ndACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F6.jpg&h=3cfee8a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果有多張船飛，妳會唔會同我一齊走呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-w_9TDNzA6Ic/Wh1whLK0AqI/AAAAAAAAP9A/3FURZ8B-fBYaCXLAkjTULMCaoSPgaPWsgCLcBGAs/s1600/7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-w_9TDNzA6Ic%2FWh1whLK0AqI%2FAAAAAAAAP9A%2F3FURZ8B-fBYaCXLAkjTULMCaoSPgaPWsgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F7.jpg&h=4b245e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我一直都以為我同何寶榮好唔同，點知原來寂寞起上嚟嗰陣，個個都係一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/---Y2Tc2mY5M/Wh1xRwR263I/AAAAAAAAP9M/TAL4a8Bg3sMe4PP6aXZ6Q_IlOslLjGpDgCLcBGAs/s1600/8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F---Y2Tc2mY5M%2FWh1xRwR263I%2FAAAAAAAAP9M%2FTAL4a8Bg3sMe4PP6aXZ6Q_IlOslLjGpDgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F8.jpg&h=bc51b443&s={SIZE}\" /> 1960年4月16號下晝三點之前嘅一分鐘妳同我喺埋一齊，因為妳我會記得嗰一分鐘，由而家開始我哋就係一分鐘嘅朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QBwr3vxB9Mg/Wh1zbvL8D9I/AAAAAAAAP9o/GNGnKEMTtTkCSu0YDi3rEgvEk3F1RQRawCLcBGAs/s1600/11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-QBwr3vxB9Mg%2FWh1zbvL8D9I%2FAAAAAAAAP9o%2FGNGnKEMTtTkCSu0YDi3rEgvEk3F1RQRawCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F11.jpg&h=ef3b1fd5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n身為保龍一族嘅情報人員，好應該神不知鬼不覺咁隱藏身份，做足啲好！大夫～我係咪有咗啫～<br />\n<br />\n喵星人的電影世界：<br />\n<a href=\"http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/11/coco-me-201711.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F11%2Fcoco-me-201711.html&d=6ELBg8tlbAmHu5TpQmocowRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=09ecb116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/11/coco-me-201711.html</a>"},{"pid":"2bc3eb944ec58e690721607640d21d358012afeb","tid":491201,"uid":40662,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3nEps6H9NlM/Wh1v1D7J9lI/AAAAAAAAP80/ChRTsidxLocOY5LQovn3FoHb6uJbZoC3ACLcBGAs/s1600/5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-3nEps6H9NlM%2FWh1v1D7J9lI%2FAAAAAAAAP80%2FChRTsidxLocOY5LQovn3FoHb6uJbZoC3ACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F5.jpg&h=7a23fb9b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咩嘢事咁邋遢呀？捽甩佢！</span>"},{"pid":"5a33b705629392a1f03854554b55b9fc8a13d708","tid":491201,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4008afc515a64f3a2e56993798d759466feab97","tid":491201,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}